name: Cgmonitor
body:
#CGMonitor
Web interface to monitor several cgminer instances

##Dependencies
Following dependencies are needed:

toml
```
$ go get github.com/BurntSushi/toml
```

Gorilla Mux
```
$ go get github.com/gorilla/mux
```
